trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref>, an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref>, or a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>, specifying the text patterns for which to search the HTTP transmission.
For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeTextBinding"></xref> class.
Gets the collection of MIME text patterns for which the HTTP transmission is searched.
For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeTextMatchCollection"></xref> representing the MIME text patterns to search for.
Specifies the URI for the XML namespace of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeTextBinding"></xref> class.
